'''Quinne Brown''' (yavutse ku ya 9 Kamena 1979) ni umukinnyi  wa firime m [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''Ouma se Slim Kind'', ''Sedona's Rule'' and ''This Is Charlotte King''. . <ref>http://www.artistconnection.co.za/artists/183/cv.pdf</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Brown yavukiye i Johannesburg, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Amaze kwiga, yize geografiya na antropologiya muri kaminuza ya Johannesburg . Yagiye i San Francisco mu 2003 gushyingura se, aho yahuriye n'umugabo we Ryan Huffman. <ref>https://www.magzter.com/article/Lifestyle/woman-home-South-Africa/Having-Children-Taught-Me-Who-I-Am</ref> Yashakanye na 2006 kandi bombi babaga i San Francisco. Nyuma abo bashakanye bimukiye i San Diego, aho babyaranye abakobwa babo bombi, Charlotte na Lara. <ref>https://www.all4women.co.za/1813181/health-and-wellness/womens-health/7de-laan-actress-doula-women-need-to-choose-their-own-birthing-experience</ref>

Mu masomo ye, Brown yabonye amahirwe yo kwinjira mu bakinnyi bikinamico ya  ''7de Laan'' . <ref>https://omny.fm/shows/the-john-maytham-show/an-hour-with-quinne-browneon-just-the-hits</ref> Muri uruhererekane, yakinnye ari ''Connie van der Lecq'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/you/Celebs/7de-laan-actress-opens-up-about-her-characters-dark-side-20190111</ref> Usibye gukina, anakora nkuwatanze ikiganiro kuri SABC2. Mu 2003, Brown yafashe ikiruhuko cy'isabato nyuma y'urupfu rwa se muri Mata 2003. <ref>https://www.netwerk24.com/huisgenoot/Bekendes/7de-laan-se-quinne-brown-kuier-in-amerika-vir-kersfees-20191217</ref>

Yakoze kandi mu ikinamico, filime no kwamamaza bishingiye kuri San Francisco. <ref>https://www.backstage.com/u/QuinneBrown/</ref> Muri 2008, yatangiye kwigisha abana mwishuri ryimikino ryabana. <ref>https://www.netwerk24.com/huisgenoot/Bekendes/splinternuwe-avontuur-vir-quinne-brown-en-manlief-ryan-20180426</ref> Nyuma yimyaka icumi muri [[Amerika]], yasubiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] hamwe numuryango. Mu mwaka wa 2016, yongeye gukina mu bakinnyi ba '7de Laan', anagaragaza imico ye 'Connie'. <ref>http://www.sabc2.co.za/sabc/home/sabc2/news/details?id=d4b593a6-7ba8-4241-a0c9-9c05cd893ea2&title=Quinne+Brown+Huffman+rejoins+the+cast+of+7de+laan</ref>

